title: Briggs and Riley Domestic Carry-On Expandable Spinner
description:
In this video we take a look at the Briggs and Riley Domestic Carry-on Expandable Spinner bag.  For more details or to place an order please visit us at Abt.com: http://www.abt.com/product/111729/Briggs-Riley-Black-Domestic-Carry-On-Expandable-Spinner-U122CXSP4.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=U122CXSP4%20_20170711

Features:
- Interior:
Cinch-down mesh garment panels keep contents from shifting and minimize wrinkling
Spacious main compartment for easy packing
Built-in tri-fold garment folder with foam roll bar neatly holds 1-2 suits and prevents wrinkling
Mesh lid zip pocket for organizing smaller accessories like socks or ties

- Exterior:
Aircraft-grade aluminum handle system with 3 stop heights
Outsider® handle provides greater interior capacity and a flat interior surface for packing so clothing arrives wrinkle-free
V-groove handle tubes are stronger and guarantee less jamming
Ballistic nylon outer fabric resists wear, moisture, dirt and abrasion.
Cushioned top carry handle for smooth handling
Four double swivel wheels for effortless 360° navigation
HideAway™ ID tag conceals personal information
Hybrid fiberglass frame is lightweight and provides flexibility, durability and shape retention
Integrated bottom fabric handle for easy lifting
Large u-zip front pocket for hassle-free access to extra items
Outsider® pocket for convenient storage of quick-access items
Reinforced, low profile protective corner guards on all 4 corners
Retractable low profile side carry handle
Self-repairing YKK zippers for smooth zipper action with lockable double zipper pulls
SpeedThru™ pocket for storage of items at security checkpoints

- Specifications:
Capacity: 2620 - 3390 cu. in./43 - 55.6 liters
Zipper: Our bags feature self-repairing, durable YKK® Racquet Coil™ zippers. Ergonomic zipper pulls. Lockable main compartment zipper pulls.
Fabric: 2520D ballistic nylon outer fabric is abrasion resistant, water repellent, color fast and self healing. Soft, durable twill lining is light-colored to easily locate packed items

- Approximate Dimensions:
Height: 22"
Width: 14"
Depth: 9"
Case: 19.5 x 14 x 8"
Outside Expanded Depth: 11.5"
